data.description:
Welcome to this spacious and inviting 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom house located at 13411 Spruce Street. This property is currently available for sale, offering a wonderful opportunity for you to make it your new home.
With a size over 3000 square feet, this house provides ample space for you and your family to comfortably spread out. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living areas, making it perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. This property boasts two cozy fireplaces, adding warmth and charm to the living spaces - one fireplace on the main living floor with the second fireplace situated in the primary bedroom. 
Situated on a lot that backs to open space, this house offers privacy and tranquility. The fully fenced yard provides a safe and secure area for children or pets to play freely.
The finished basement offers additional flexible living space that can be customized to suit your needs. 
The covered patio is perfect for outdoor relaxation and enjoyment. 
All appliances are included with this property, providing convenience and ease as you settle into your new home.

Located in a desirable neighborhood, this house offers proximity to schools, parks, shopping centers, and other amenities. Commuting is made easy with convenient access to major highways and public transportation options.
Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fantastic property. Schedule a viewing today and let us help you make this house your dream home! 
Jessica Arguello -  720-514-3897
